{"tid":383962,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"有無人明白愛一個人愛得太緊要嘅感受","createTime":"2017-09-02T02:07:54.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-03T00:53:11.000Z","uid":136940,"like":33,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"ff6d26b3a061869783053c378572de970370f330","tid":383962,"uid":136940,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-02T02:07:54.000Z","msg":"當你同佢就黎分開好耐 你個心會掛到仆街<br />\n想死<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/18.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n電話一震就諗係咪佢 好緊張<br />\n個人完全瞓唔到 淨係想佢係你隔離<br />\n<br />\n我知你睇到架 希望你知我嘅心底說話啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n有無巴絲都係咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"457639631d21443574bcd5fb994986064d1963c4","tid":383962,"uid":123647,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-02T02:09:08.000Z","msg":"有呀 <br />\n<br />\n分咗手了<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0b89e123a602623fa8c98883de444aa8f69fb28a","tid":383962,"uid":139109,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-02T02:11:08.000Z","msg":"見住自己鐘意既人po同女朋友開心煮飯仔相 個心痛到 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"107f0251a47cc33a397fa7e03c3658961d02b987","tid":383962,"uid":828,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-02T02:14:12.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>見住自己鐘意既人po同女朋友開心煮飯仔相 個心痛到 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6d1be213c2af19bdb0176c34227182b3ee5e2d05","tid":383962,"uid":139109,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-02T02:17:53.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>見住自己鐘意既人po同女朋友開心煮飯仔相 個心痛到 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n點解個個唔可以係我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgm