"tid":383962,"uid":125589,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-02T10:01:47.000Z","msg":"佢同我講佢愛人多過愛自己 最後同咗佢一齊之後 佢只愛自己 得我一個愛得太緊要<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6d972db48b583dd42d9ba78ef0d5b766eda3467d","tid":383962,"uid":140917,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-02T10:36:32.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有呀 不過睇開左 冇聯絡 唔想佢再係我世界出現</blockquote><br />\n應該過左好耐先調整得返呢個心態 <br />\n不過最大鑊都係影響晒以後既愛情觀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"029d21c30370bc893a5cb50af0216a4a03664dca","tid":383962,"uid":99001,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-02T14:31:55.000Z","msg":"愛佢愛到冇左自己 最後比佢飛埋 <br />\n<br />\n最後睇住佢開開心心搵下個 自己日日抑鬱"},{"pid":"34cb94798655d973ba6c100c7446c06fd1782c78","tid":383962,"uid":127116,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-02T15:12:44.000Z","msg":"樓上個個都講哂我心聲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n明明先一齊左四個月<br />\n都分左四個月差唔多五個月<br />\n點解仲咁掛住佢咁唔捨得佢<br />\n明明佢對我又唔係特別好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f7ee037690fe2ddaba9ab5634878edfeeeea09dc","tid":383962,"uid":81408,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-02T17:34:40.000Z","msg":"我明 我真係明<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n佢唔浪漫 唔講甜言蜜語 唔花時間陪我 <br />\nEven佢連我鍾意啲咩佢都應該唔知<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n同佢一齊好似神交咁 <br />\n佢講過既誠諾 可能由頭到尾上心既只有我一個<br />\n可能係初戀 可能期望好高 太過渴望得到佢既愛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n其實我連係佢身邊存在過既證明都無<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我都唔知點解我咁愛 愛到山窮水盡無錢都想買野比佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n愛到晚晚都諗起佢而失眠 愛佢多過愛自己<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n愛佢真係好痛 一諗起佢都覺得痛<br />\n的起心肝 呢段時間好好學習緊一個人 <br />\n好好學習唔再愛佢 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f41ab59775f4f4daf046d3411314c8445333d5e3","tid":383962,"uid":133077,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-02T18:34:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7ba0599a21f1227d6663acd3c8a418cd8048d4de","tid":383962,"uid":65400,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-02T18:55:20.000Z","msg":"MK POST"},{"pid":"bdff00e11e86e81c5634a82d2dc92620ad477d73","tid":383962,"uid":75887,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-02T21:48:35.000Z","msg":"我明 <br />\nlong d <br />\n每日都好想知你做咩<br />\n當又怕你話我問長問短<br />\n好想你日日都宅係屋企<br />\n咁就唔會有人掂你<br />\n但你又會好悶<br />\n你出街又好怕你同其他男仔一齊<br />\n好驚其他人搶走你<br />\n你有問題 我唔可以係你身邊<br />\n幫唔到你 好心痛<br />\n隔兩個鐘都未覆我就不斷諗你做緊咩<br />\n你話我地一齊之前 我好高冷<br />\n依家我比你搞到 每分每秒都掛住你<br />\n<br />\n夜🐱"},{"pid":"f4325c34f1d750654e77ae3008dcf49894b26c07","tid":383962,"uid":9348,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-02T23:45:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"08e56e782ece1f54e3bb325070d5de2375dec106","tid":383962,"uid":19989,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-02T23:49:31.000Z","msg":"然後太著緊太chur對方就會走<br />\n利申 就chur到佢分手"},{"pid":"b7e76fcee6e863d95ae279d9b8213cbf67ff08c1","tid":383962,"uid":136940,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-03T00:31:16.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>然後太著緊太chur對方就會走<br />\n利申 就chur到佢分手</blockquote><br />\n希望黎緊唔好有呢一日<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ac04d61bb85883b1d6aa1855f77fc51fe0d8a265","tid